import lmql
from dataclasses import dataclass

@dataclass
class Employer:
    employer_name: str
    location: str

@dataclass
class Person:
    name: str
    age: int
    employer: Employer
    job: str

argmax
    "Alice is a 21 years old and works as an engineer at LMQL Inc in Zurich, Switzerland: [p]\n"
    "The name is {p.name} and she works in {p.employer.location}."
from 
    "chatgpt" 
where 
    type(p) is Person
